{"title":"父亲在检阅“队伍”","authors":["毕东海"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲在检阅“队伍”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕东海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着田埂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲一遍遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这头走向那头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面前茂密青纱帐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如士兵的方阵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而父亲则俨然是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身经百战的将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这飒爽秋天里举行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛大阅兵式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风声浩荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奏响雄壮军乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲倒背手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逐棵逐棵地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"审视自己的千军万马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪棵庄稼站歪了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪棵庄稼无精打采"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都逃不过父亲锥子般眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他会侧身几步走进队列里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毫不客气地用锄头和铁锨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给他们下达立正命令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让他们保持坚挺姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时父亲会停下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和某棵庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长久对视"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛要透过这棵庄稼瞳仁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洞悉所有庄稼的心理活动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌握它们的精神状态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲朝棵粗壮的庄稼走去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先是歪着脑袋打量一番"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接着亲切地拉拉庄稼手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又突然兴奋地拍下庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里不停地啧啧赞叹着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼们都挺胸昂首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威武静穆整齐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向头罩白肚巾的父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充满敬意地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行庄严注目礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这军容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这士气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这魂魄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这阵势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲感到踏实了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲嘿嘿笑了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论还有什么风暴灾难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个个都不是孬种呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不会三摇两晃地趴下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打胜秋收这一仗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲有十足的信心"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}